{
  "stem": "210.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from that time, they were really scared to go out in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father just stayed in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was the one that really-- and my brother and sister were much younger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they weren't of much help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was the one that really worked and did whatever I could to help the family out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, this was-- this was about, let's see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, my father-- my father got sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR4 SECONDS] this was in, I think in-- this was already shortly before-- before the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --anyway.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mine-- my uncle was still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they opened up a factory in our city where the temple, the [NON-ENGLISH] and the [NON-ENGLISH] used to be.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they made a factory there where they made German uniforms for nurses, for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my uncle, had to-- you know, since he was a tailor, he and some-- and my cousins, and some other people, were working there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they-- and they paid them very little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in order not for them to be deported, so they worked, and they were like safe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One day there was like-- my uncle came in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said that they-- there were like, you know, all these rumors-- all these rumors going around.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was maybe 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the rumors were that they were gonna take the girls away, you know, all young girls, that they're gonna take them away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my uncle, since he was in the factory at that time, he took me to his house.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
